This product includes software developed at third parties, vendored under
vendor/ subdirectories. Each vendored tree preserves its upstream LICENSE
and, where applicable, MODEL_PROVENANCE.md. Specific provenance and the
exact upstream commit shas are recorded in vendor/*/UPSTREAM_COMMIT files.

- vendor/concordia-ptx/  — PTX parser from the Concordia GPU compilation
  framework. See vendor/concordia-ptx/UPSTREAM_COMMIT for the exact sha.

- vendor/gemma-generated/ — Runtime and mapping JSON descriptors from the
  Gemma FPGA artifact bundle. Preserves upstream LICENSE and
  MODEL_PROVENANCE.md. See vendor/gemma-generated/UPSTREAM_COMMIT for the
  exact sha.
